abstract: Rocket attack kills six protesters demonstrating in Benghazi, Libya, against United Nations proposal to resolve Libya's political standoff.
lead_paragraph: The group had gathered to protest a United Nations proposal for a unity government to end a political crisis.

headline.main: Libya: 6 Killed as Rockets Hit Protesters in Benghazi
headline.print_headline: Middle East; Libya: 6 Killed as Rockets Hit Protesters in Benghazi
